{"lastModified":1768317507494,"uri":"c::18121026674::vessel::94397b30-da96-11f0-99bd-a740c9baf0c0","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Cannigione, Costa Smeralda, Sardinia\n\nEnjoy an exclusive experience combining comfort, elegance, and breathtaking views of the Costa Smeralda. Discover Sardinia from a unique perspective aboard the Aquila 44 Power Catamaran , available for charter in Cannigione, in the heart of the Costa Smeralda .\n\nThis luxury catamaran combines innovation, power, and comfort to offer you an unforgettable experience at sea. With its spacious interior and exterior , the Aquila 44 is ideal for spending days dedicated to relaxation, adventure, and conviviality. The living areas and panoramic terraces offer 360° views and are perfect for sharing special moments with family and friends. Equipped with two Volvo Penta Diesel engines strategically positioned behind the living areas, the catamaran ensures quiet and smooth sailing , reducing vibration and noise. Thanks to the advanced digital controls and the joystick for the double bow thruster , every maneuver is simple and intuitive, even for small crews or couples.\n\nAttention to detail is what makes the Aquila 44 a true gem: refined interiors, high-quality materials, and spaces designed to offer comfort, safety, and freedom at every moment of your cruise. Whether you want to explore the islands of the La Maddalena Archipelago , discover Porto Cervo, or enjoy the turquoise sea in complete privacy, the Aquila 44 is the perfect choice for experiencing the best of Sardinia from the sea. Book your Aquila 44 Power Catamaran charter in Cannigione now and enjoy an exclusive experience on the Costa Smeralda, combining luxury, relaxation, and pristine nature.","blueprint":{"name":"AQUILA 44","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::94397b30-da96-11f0-99bd-a740c9baf0c0::assets::0ab76d10-da99-11f0-bb78-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::94397b30-da